message: "If you use CareerOS in your work, please cite it as below."
title: "CareerOS"
abstract: >-
  A Claude Code-native, LaTeX-first CV and cover-letter builder fused with a
  job-application pipeline that learns from a user's own CV and cover letter to
  produce tailored, ATS-safe documents. Runs locally with no server and no API key.
type: software
authors:
